/* Description */
A CakePHP plugin that allows for creating custom find types by simply adding a new method to the model.

/* Install */
1) Download the plugin to /app/plugin/find

2) Include the FindAppModel in your app_model.php
App::import('Model', 'Find.app_model');

3) Have your AppModel extend FindAppModel

/* Usage */
1) Create find types with the pattern:
$this->Model->find('custom');

2) In your model:
function __findCustom($options) {
  //do find here
}